{"title":"伟人和一座山","authors":["肖川"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":2,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟人和一座山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路饥寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路血火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路征尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从韶山起步的汉子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和他率领的一群旧世界叛逆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被围剿被诛伐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得不迂回北上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雁用翅膀寻找归宿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他扳着指头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听指纹讲述走过的曲折"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用红旗和长缨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运筹前程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说，当时下着小雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深重的古塬更加晦暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他却望见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高的天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淡淡的云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象着民族的未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一座平凡的山谱成光辉词章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尔后，以遒劲的笔锋使之驰动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他无意当诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只想做真正的好汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他生命的历程就是长征的历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他跋涉的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有翻不尽的山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缚不完的苍龙"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}